    {
      "id": "cli-nb:2cd298b815",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Glue commands for AI coding assistants. Each subcommand reads the\nassistant's hook payload on stdin and writes the assistant's expected response\non stdout. These are wired up by the assistant's plugin, not run by hand."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Limkommandoer for AI-kodeassistenter. Hver underkommando leser assistentens\nhook-nyttelast på stdin og skriver svaret assistenten forventer på stdout.\nDisse kobles opp av assistentens tillegg og kjøres ikke for hånd."
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "cli-nb:3591fcab96",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Export the TM to TMX 1.4 format. Each entry is written as a single\n<tu> with one <tuv> per language variant present (or the subset requested\nvia --locales). Inline markup is preserved as TMX <ph>/<bpt>/<ept>/<it>/<hi>.\n\nBy default all variants on every entry are emitted. Pass --locales to\nrestrict to a subset (comma-separated)."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Eksporter oversettelsesminnet til TMX 1.4-format. Hver enhet skrives som én\n<tu> med én <tuv> per språkvariant som finnes (eller utvalget som er bedt om\nmed --locales). Inline-merking bevares som TMX <ph>/<bpt>/<ept>/<it>/<hi>.\n\nSom standard skrives alle varianter på hver enhet. Bruk --locales for å\nbegrense til et utvalg (kommaseparert)."
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "cli-nb:360567a464",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Generate a shell completion script for the specified shell.\n\nTo load completions:\n\nBash:\n  $ source <(kapi completion bash)\n  # Or install permanently:\n  $ kapi completion bash > /etc/bash_completion.d/kapi\n\nZsh:\n  $ source <(kapi completion zsh)\n  # Or install permanently:\n  $ kapi completion zsh > \"${fpath[1]}/_kapi\"\n\nFish:\n  $ kapi completion fish | source\n  # Or install permanently:\n  $ kapi completion fish > ~/.config/fish/completions/kapi.fish\n\nPowerShell:\n  PS> kapi completion powershell | Out-String | Invoke-Expression\n"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Generer et skript for skallfullføring for det angitte skallet.\n\nSlik laster du inn fullføringene:\n\nBash:\n  $ source <(kapi completion bash)\n  # Eller installer permanent:\n  $ kapi completion bash > /etc/bash_completion.d/kapi\n\nZsh:\n  $ source <(kapi completion zsh)\n  # Eller installer permanent:\n  $ kapi completion zsh > \"${fpath[1]}/_kapi\"\n\nFish:\n  $ kapi completion fish | source\n  # Eller installer permanent:\n  $ kapi completion fish > ~/.config/fish/completions/kapi.fish\n\nPowerShell:\n  PS> kapi completion powershell | Out-String | Invoke-Expression\n"
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
