    {
      "id": "cli-nb:ac32d792a8",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Manage project terminology.\n\nA termbase is a glossary of approved terms stored as a SQLite database.\nUse these commands to import, export, look up, and manage terms.\n\nResource location (mutually exclusive):\n  --name <n>      Named termbase in KAPI_HOME (~/.config/kapi/termbases/<n>.db)\n  --local         Termbase in current directory (./termbase.db)\n  --file <path>   Explicit file path\n\nDefault (no flag): same as --local (uses ./termbase.db)."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Administrer prosjektterminologi.\n\nEn termbase er en ordliste med godkjente termer lagret som en SQLite-database.\nBruk disse kommandoene til å importere, eksportere, slå opp og administrere termer.\n\nRessursplassering (gjensidig utelukkende):\n  --name <n>      Navngitt termbase i KAPI_HOME (~/.config/kapi/termbases/<n>.db)\n  --local         Termbase i gjeldende katalog (./termbase.db)\n  --file <path>   Eksplisitt filsti\n\nStandard (uten flagg): samme som --local (bruker ./termbase.db)."
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "cli-nb:afbe04022b",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "List available processing tools"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "List tilgjengelige behandlingsverktøy"
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "cli-nb:b2c371bf84",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "An import session is created every time a TMX file is imported.\nEach session records the file's SHA-256 hash, TMX header metadata, and the\nnumber of entries imported. Origins on TM entries point back to the session\nthat added them so you can filter the TM by import source."
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "En importøkt opprettes hver gang en TMX-fil importeres.\nHver økt registrerer filens SHA-256-hasj, TMX-headerens metadata og antall\nimporterte enheter. Opphav på TM-enheter peker tilbake til økten som la dem\ntil, slik at du kan filtrere oversettelsesminnet på importkilde."
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "cli-nb:b612264c3d",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Apply a returned bilingual file (.klz/XLIFF/PO) back onto the project source"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Flett en returnert tospråklig fil (.klz/XLIFF/PO) tilbake inn i prosjektkilden"
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "cli-nb:b7dce813d8",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "Scaffold a brand voice profile YAML to fill in (optionally seeded from a starter pack)"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "Lag et utkast til merkevarestemmeprofil i YAML (eventuelt basert på en startpakke)"
          }
        ]
      },
      "created": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z",
      "updated": "2026-06-11T08:02:59Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "cli-nb:b8e7b32cfe",
      "hintSrcLang": "en",
      "variants": {
        "en": [
          {
            "text": "EXTENSIONS"
          }
        ],
        "nb": [
          {
            "text": "FILENDELSER"
          }
        ]
      },
